text=!!! Interacció%0a* [['''Gerstner, Karl, '''Designing probrammes''',1964''' -> https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BxA8se8r6JKZdjNoT2pGcDlwcms/view?usp=sharing]]%0a* Groß Benedikt, et al.'''Generative Design''' Princeton Architectural Press, 2019.%0a* Reas Casey, McWilliams Chandler, LUST. '''Form & Code''' Princeton Architectural Press. 2012%0a* Joshua Noble, '''Programming Interactivity''', Published January 2012, O'Reilly.%0a* Shneiderman, B. i Plaisant, C., '''Diseño de interacción de usuario. Estrategias para una interacción persona-computadora efectiva''' Pearson-Addison Wesley, Madrid, 2006%0a* R. Klanten, S. Ehmann, V. Hanschke, '''Touch of code. Interactive installations and experiencies''', 2011, Gestalten%0a* André Knörig, [[http://andreknoerig.de/portfolio/35/bin/Knoerig08_DesignToolsDesign.pdf | '''Design tools design''']], 2008%0a* Jan Barth, Roman Stefan Grasy, Jochen Leinberger, Mark Lukas, Markus Lorenz Schilling. [[http://prototypinginterfaces.com/ | Prototyping Interfaces: Interaktives Skizzieren mit vvvv, Gebundene Ausgabe ]]%0a* [['''Free Art Bureau'''-> http://freeartbureau.org/]]%0a*[['''A gentle introduction to coding by making generative art'''->https://medium.com/@ibrahim.serafy/a-gentle-introduction-to-coding-by-making-generative-art-c7f0a7b744a6]]%0a* Donald A. Norman, [[http://www.loop.la/descargas/disenho/Psicologia_objetos_cotidianos%2520-%2520Donald%2520Norman.pdf | '''Psicologia de los objetos cotidianos''']]%0a* [[http://www.press.uchicago.edu/ucp/books/book/chicago/M/bo3637992.html |'''Metaphors We Live By''']], George Lakoff and Mark Johnson%0a* [[https://retoricaprofesional.files.wordpress.com/2013/03/mcluhan-marshall-el-medio-es-el-mensaje.pdf| '''El medio es el mensaje''']], Marshall McLuhan%0a%0a!!! Aesthetics%0a*[['''Drawing with computers'''->http://mgwilson.com/Drawing%2520with%2520Computers.pdf]], Wilson, Mark%0a*[['''Exploring art throught data'''->https://www.artnome.com/]], blog, Jason Bailey%0a*[['''Estètica relacional'''->http://www.perrorabioso.com/textos/Estetica-relacional-Nicolas-Bourriaud.pdf]], Nicolas Bourriaud%0a*[['''Obra abierta'''->https://direccionmultiple.files.wordpress.com/2012/08/eco_umberto-obra_abierta.pdf]], Umberto Eco%0a*[['''El arte como experiencia'''->http://archivos.liccom.edu.uy/Figuras/Dewey,%2520John%2520-%2520El%2520arte%2520como%2520experiencia.pdf]], John Dewey%0a*[['''The book of shaders'''->http://thebookofshaders.com/]], Patricio González Vivo and Jen Lowe%0a*[['''New Directions in Digital Poetry'''->http://www.bloomsbury.com/us/new-directions-in-digital-poetry-9781441115911/]], C.T. Funhouser%0a*[['''Cybertext Poetics, The Critical Landscape of New Media Literary Theory'''->http://www.bloomsbury.com/us/cybertext-poetics-9781441118202/]], Markku Eskilenen%0a* [[https://es.scribd.com/doc/196913083/La-estetica-del-error-en-la-edad-digital | La estética del error en la edad digital]], Pedro Ajo%0a*[['''When the machine made art'''->https://azprojectsblog.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/when-the-machine-made-art_-the-troubled-hi-grant-d-taylor.pdf ]], Frand D. Taylor, Bloomsbury%0a* [[http://vk.com/doc1840617_164445629?hash=c7fc1cb074207c419d&dl=28aabb49a7217e1962 |'''Emotional design every day''']], Donald Norman%0a* [[http://fffff.at/TheManual/The_FAT_Manual_Link_Editions_2013.pdf | '''Free Art and Technologic Manual''']]%0a* [[https://www.generativehut.com/ | Generative Hut]]%0a%0a!!! Processing%0a* [[Greenberg, Ira. Processing. Creative Coding and Computational Art->https://www.trilhas.iar.unicamp.br/curso/processing/processing_creative_coding.pdf]]%0a* [[Shiffman, Daniel. Learning Processing A Beginners Guide To Programming Images, Animation & Interaction->https://archive.org/details/LearningProcessing/page/n59/mode/2up]]%0a* [[Shiffman, Daniel. The nature of code-> https://natureofcode.com/book/chapter-4-particle-systems/]]%0a* [[Taller de creació d'identiat generativa->https://julian-perez.com/wiki/doku.php?id=talleridgenp5]], Julián Pérez%0a* Casey Reas and Ben Fry, '''Getting Started with Processing''', Published June 2010, O'Reilly Media. 208 pages. Paperback%0a* Hartmut Bohnacker, Benedikt Gross, Julia Laub, and Claudius Lazzeroni, '''Generative Design''' August 2012, Princeton Architectural Press%0a* Jan Vantomme, '''Processing 2: Creative Programming Cookbook''',Published September 2012, PACKT. 350 pages. Paperback and eBook%0a* [[http://issuu.com/jpagecorrigan/docs/type-code_yeohyun-ahn |  '''Type + code''']]%0a* Shiffman, Daniel. [[http://natureofcode.com/|The nature of code]]%0a*  Derek Runberg, [[https://www.nostarch.com/sparkfunprocessing| SparkFun Guide to Processing. Create Interactive Art with Code]]%0a* [[http://generative-typografie.de/ | Generative typografie]]%0a* Tutorial: [[http://hello.processing.org/ | Hello Processing]]%0a* Tutorial: [[http://p5art.tumblr.com/tutorials | Experiments in Processing]]%0a* Workshop: [[http://visualizing-data.org | Visualizing Data]]%0a* Workshop: [[http://formcode.org | form&code]]%0a* Workshop: [[http://multisensory-data.com | Multisensory Data]]%0a* [[http://assets.surattack.com/files/processing_cheat_sheet_english.pdf | Processing Cheat sheet]]%0a* [[https://necessarydisorder.wordpress.com/ | Tutorial distortion or smoke effect on parametric curves, and more general loop techniques]]%0a* [[http://www.codingmath.com/ | '''Coding Math''']]%0a%0a!!! Arduino%0a* Banzi, M, '''Getting started with Arduino''', O’Reilly, 2009%0a* Tom Igoe, '''Making Things Talk: Using Sensors, Networks, and Arduino to see, hear, and feel your world''' Published September 2011, O'Reilly%0a* Greg Borenstein, '''Making Things See: 3D vision with Kinect, Processing, Arduino, and MakerBot''',Published February 2012, O'Reilly%0a* Karvinen, K, '''Make Arduino bots and gadgets''', 2011, O’Reilly %0a* Morrison, R, '''Practical electronics : a self-teaching guide'''%0a* Torrente, O,'''Arduino.Curso práctico de formación''', RC libros, 2013%0a* [[http://www.artinteractivo.com/tutorial-arduino | '''arteinteractivo: manual arduino''']]%0a* [[http://castilla.verkstad.cc/es/ |'''Creative Technologies, tutorial (es)''']]%0a* [[https://itp.nyu.edu/physcomp/|'''ITP Physical computing''']]%0a* McComb, Gordon '''Electronics for dummies''', Hoboken, N.J. : Wiley, cop. 2005%0a%0a!!! Metodologia%0a* [[http://lab.cccb.org/ca/x-cap-a-un-nou-atles-del-disseny/ | FLOGIA, Efraín, Cap a un nou atles del disseny ]]%0a* [[http://ocs.editorial.upv.es/index.php/ILUSTRAFIC/ILUSTRAFIC2015/paper/viewFile/342/1153 | SÁNCHEZ , Dionisio, El valor de la metodología en el proceso como metodología proyectual]]%0a* [[http://www.fadu.edu.uy/estetica-diseno-ii/files/2015/03/Anna-Calvera-De-lo-bello-de-las-cosas.pdf | CALVERA, Anna, De lo bello de las cosas. Materiales para una estética del diseño. Barcelona: Editorial Gustavo Gili, p. 19]]%0a* [[http://reader.lgru.net/pages/index/ | '''Considering your tools''']]%0a* [[http://printingcode.runemadsen.com/ | '''Programming design systems''']]%0a%0a!!! Fonts bibliogràfics%0a*[['''Institute of network cultures'''->http://networkcultures.org/publications/#all]]%0a*[['''Cybernetics Library'''->https://cybernetics.social/]]%0a*[['''Libertario Library'''->http://libertar.io/lab/materiales/material/texto/]]%0a%0a!!! Publicacions científiques %0a* [[http://neural.it/| '''neural''']]%0a* [[http://journals.uoc.edu/index.php/artnodes/issue/archive |'''Journal on art, science and technology''']]%0a
